aimed against the king and Nd5 is not possible anymore.}) 11... O-O 12. Rad1
Qd7 (12... Ne5 13. b3 {Preventing Nc4.}) 13. Bh6 $14 {Exchanging the
dark-squared bishops. White has a small but pleasant advantage, while Black
