with Qd6, the idea is to play Bg5 next and then Rd1.}) 10... Bg7 11. e5 dxe5
12. Qxe5+ Kf8 13. Qe2 $16 {Black has a lot of weaknesses and Black's king is
uncastled.}) (7... Nf6 8. Qe2 {Transposes to 6.. .Nf6.}) 8. Nxc6 bxc6 9. b3 $1
