O-O-O Nc5 13. Qe3 (13. Qg3 $5 {White can start with this move too.} Bh4 14. Qe3
) 13... Re8 14. f4 Bf8 15. Rhe1 $16 {g4-g5 is an idea, or White can play Kb1
