7... bxc6 (7... Bxc6 {Transposes to 4...Bd7.}) 8. Qf3 c5 (8... Rb8 9. b3 c5 (
9... Be7 10. Bb2 $16) 10. Nf5 Bxf5 11. exf5 d5 12. Bb2 d4 13. O-O-O Be7 14. g4
